services:
AGM Renovations offers Complete basement and Bathroom renovations packages from the professional design through the professional cleaning including:

Drywall- We employ only professional drywall installers and our goal is deliver complete satisfaction to each and every client with the quality of our workmanship and our prompt, reliable service.
    
Taping- Our drywall taping techniques will bring a high quality smooth finish, with a level of excellence you will take pride in.

Painting- We include all wall priming, painting of ceilings, baseboards, casing, crown and cove moldings into our basement construction packages
    
High Grade Laminate Flooring- is standard in our basement renovations packages.

Tiling- Shower, bathroom, or kitchenette tiling will be done by professional tile installers who are employed directly by AGM. A 2 year unlimited warranty is provided to you standard when you finish your basement with AGM
   
Plumbing- Our licensed plumbers will ensure that no problem is left unsolved and you can be sure that any drain or other plumbing defects left by the original house builder will be fixed effectively.

Electrical- We are committed to providing fully licensed electrician service as part of our standard package. Should you ever require an electrical certificate when you decide to sell your property, we will be happy to provide it to you

Granstone is an Ottawa-based leading provider of custom kitchen, basement and  bathroom renovations as well as fabricators and installers of stone countertops.  
We can do anything you require from full custom cabinets, flooring, backsplash, and countertops.   We have also recently added an electrical division with certified master electricians on staff.

Granstone employees approach each and every one of their projects as if it were their own. We strive to create a professional environment for our customers in order to ensure that every experience is a positive one. 

Should you have at any point in time some questions, please do not hesitate to contact our knowledgeable staff:
-via phone (613-733-0391)  
-email (info@granstone.ca), 
or best come visit us at our Ottawa showroom located at 17 Enterprise Ave Unit I.

profile:
OGC - Ottawa General Contractors are leaders as Ottawa's design and build renovation experts. Specializing in home renovations, new and custom home construction as well as home design. With our project management and coordination, we're able to efficiently juggle more jobs, large and small, without dropping the ball. 

Ottawa General Contractors are an accredited business with the Ottawa BBB and our CEO, Moe Abbas is a former member of the board of directors for the Better Business Bureau (BBB).. Our skills and expert service has allowed us to expand to other cities in Canada including Vancouver and Calgary in less than 8 years making us one of the fastest growing construction companies. 

We offer warranty following the Tarion warranty guidelines for all our renovations and construction projects. We also have a design center and in house designers available to help you design and build your home. With over 50 years of experience, our team has the knowledge, the tools, the skill-set and the resources to give you the best value for your dollar at unbeatable service. 

We at Ottawa General Contractors understand that you are looking for value with your renovation services. Trust our team to do it right the first time! Call us directly at (613) 225-9991!

Visit our website for all our credentials and more information.

profile:
Magnolia Construction prides itself on the ability to listen and anticipate wants and needs. That’s what makes us exceptional at customizing our services to the unique situation of each and every client. We guide your vision through the entire renovation process and ensure that we are on the same page as to the best way to achieve it.

Our team of designers and builders brings expertise in a wide variety of aspects in home remodelling, and our track record of customer satisfaction earns us repeat business and referrals. You’ll find us as attentive and courteous in customer service as in the remodelling work itself.

We’ve transformed many a kitchen in Ottawa, with renovations ranging from islands and new counter tops to knocking down walls and changing the entire dynamic to a more contemporary space. Our extensive experience in kitchen renovations means you’re getting highly skilled craftsmanship to execute an exquisite transformation. Our clients give us rave reviews and have great things to say about the renovations we’ve done for the kitchens and other living spaces.

Our bathroom renovations deliver quality results, on time and on budget. We’ll work with you to create an upgraded bathroom that makes you want to linger for a while, light a candle and relax. We’ve remodeled countless bathrooms in Ottawa homes, from counters and sinks to showers & tubs to tile floors. We leave no stone unturned when we executive a renovation, keeping your full satisfaction in mind at every measurement, cut and fitting.

Magnolia will transform your basement from “blah” to “wow.” We’ll work with you to design and deliver a functional, livable basement space that your family (or your tenant) will truly enjoy. We have a knack for translating visions into reality. Talk to Magnolia about how we can work together to build a dream basement. When it comes to basements there’s no need to aim low. You deserve the best quality renovation. Magnolia can make that happen.

profile:
Estra Flooring has been serving the Ottawa community with uncompromising quality and exceptional customer service in the flooring industry since 1971. Now in our second generation, we continue to combine old world artisanship with the latest in flooring technology, with a wide variety of styles and products to accommodate a vast spectrum of home and commercial décor.

Our portfolio includes a number of notable and prestigious projects including hardwood flooring at the main function room at Rideau Hall, 24 Sussex Drive, the Rideau Club, the Committee Room on Parliament Hill and all the hardwood flooring at the National Gallery of Canada including the Rideau Street Chapel which has been reassembled there as a permanent exhibit.

Pre-Finished and Unfinished Wood Installation - simple and complex installations.
Sanding and Staining - change the mood and color of your floors, or renew the look of worn out existing hardwood floors.

Screen and Coat - refresh the sheen and the glamour, removes existing finish replaces it for a much cleaner and fresher look.

Our specialties include:

Custom Hardwood including rare & exotic woods,

Solid & Engineered,

Laminates, Cork, Bamboo

Ceramic Tile, Glass Tile

Luxury Vinyl Tile

Carpet and Carpet Tile

Condo (sound absorbent) floors

Sales, Service, Custom Designs, Free on site Estimates.

Residential –  primarily our business comes from our valued residential clients. We offer the utmost in friendly and practical advice, making sure that whatever your budget, we can make your dreams come true.

Commercial – Estra Flooring has maintained special relationships with Ottawa’s most prestigious architects, designers, builders and agencies such as Ottawa Community Housing as a result of our goal to achieve the best result as dictated by our commercial partners' expertise.

From the Rideau Hall to your home, the service we provide is of unparalleled quality.

Please visit our showroom located at 439 Preston Street, Ottawa, Ontario K1S 4N5

Monday through Saturday, Office:  613-233-0149                          

At Estra Flooring the coffee and hospitality is always on!

profile:
Tirenio Parging has been proudly offering our professional parging services in Ottawa for over 45 years. We were founded on the principles of excellence, quality, and trust. With our high-quality, efficient, and affordable services, we offer our clients the best value for their hard-earned money

OUR MISSION
To ensure that every property owner in Ottawa can not only afford to protect their foundation, but also to have access to Ottawa’s best parging group.

OUR VALUES
We value each of our clients and we will do everything to satisfy you!

OUR VISION
To become the undisputed leader of all parging companies in Ottawa.

BRIEF HISTORY:
In hopes of a more prosperous future, Cosimo Repaci immigrated to Canada from Italy approximately 50 years ago. While he had little more than the shirt on his back to start, his strong work ethic earned him an apprenticeship with one of Ottawa’s best parging companies.

After mastering the trade and perfecting his craft, Cosimo founded Tirenio Cement & Stucco LTD, whose name is inspired by the Tyrrhenian Sea, in 1970’s.

As a direct result of his solid people skills and outstanding skills, Cosimo quickly became Ottawa’s go-to man for parging and stucco services. Not surprisingly, he secured contracts with most of Ottawa’s leading builders — Caivan Communities, Cardel Homes, Claridge Homes, Mattamy Homes, Omega Homes, Phoenix Homes, Richcraft, Urbandale — and proudly served tens of thousands of satisfied customers before he retired and passed down his business to his eldest son Vincenzo Repaci.

Since taking over his father’s business, Vince has continued to build on his father’s legacy and cement Tirenio Parging LTD as the undisputed parging leader in the Ottawa region. In addition to securing new partnerships, he has significantly increased the efficiency of operations. Under Vincenzo’s leadership, his 7 member crew do over 5000 new homes per season.
